main event: An observer sighted a yellow-oval shaped object moving in a zigzag pattern in Ventnor, New Jersey on 13 May 1967.
interesting points: The sighting occurred over a period of 5 minutes., The observer recorded the object at a course of 135 degrees., The report was made by a civilian., The request for additional information and photographs was sent to the Air Force., The conclusion of the report indicated insufficient data due to lack of clarity.
